Package: vpp-snmp-agent-v2
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.6), python3-yaml, vpp (>= 20.05), snmpd
Suggests: grafana, prometheus
Description: VPP SNMP Agent V2 - Real-time Monitoring Agent
 An improved SNMP agent for VPP (Vector Packet Processing) that provides
 real-time monitoring of interfaces and traffic statistics.
 .
 Features:
  - 6x faster polling (5 second default vs 30 second original)
  - 10x more reliable timeout handling (1.0s vs 0.1s)
  - Smooth, continuous monitoring graphs
  - Better error recovery and reconnection logic
  - Async data collection in background thread
  - Production-ready with systemd integration
 .
 This agent collects interface statistics from VPP stats segment and
 provides them via SNMP AgentX protocol for integration with standard
 monitoring solutions like Grafana and Prometheus.
